  'banff-skiing-guide': `
<p>With three world-class resorts collectively known as <strong>SkiBig3</strong>, Banff offers some of the best skiing in North America. Here's your complete guide to hitting the slopes.</p>

<h2>The Three Resorts Compared</h2>

<h3>Sunshine Village</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Terrain:</strong> 3,358 acres across three mountains</li>
<li><strong>Vertical:</strong> 1,070m</li>
